[{"id":"VR442172","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Consider the following class definition.</p>\n<div class=\"standalone_code style:1\">\n<p class=\"code_line\">public class Box</p>\n<p class=\"code_line\">{</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">private double weight;</p>\n<p class=\"code_line\"> </p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">/** Postcondition: weight is initialized to w. */</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">public Box(double w)</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">{</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:6\">/* implementation not shown */</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">}</p>\n<p class=\"code_line\"> </p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">public double getWeight()</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">{</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:6\">return weight;</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">}</p>\n<p class=\"code_line\"> </p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">public void addWeight(double aw)</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">{</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:6\">/* <span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic\">missing statement</span> */</p>\n<p class=\"code_line indent:3\">}</p>\n<p class=\"code_line\">}</p>\n</div>\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">The following code segment, which appears in a class other than <span class=\"inline_code\">Box</span>,<span> </span>is intended to create a <span class=\"inline_code\">Box</span> object <span class=\"inline_code\">b1</span> with a weight of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2.2\"><math alttext=\"2.2\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2.2</mn></math></span></span> units and then increase the weight of <span class=\"inline_code\">b1</span> by <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1.5\"><math alttext=\"1.5\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1.5</mn></math></span></span> units.</p>\n<div class=\"standalone_code style:1\">\n<p class=\"code_line\">Box b1 = new Box(2.2);</p>\n<p class=\"code_line\">b1.addWeight(1.5);</p>\n</div>\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following statements could replace <span class=\"inline_code\">/*</span> <span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic\">missing statement</span> <span class=\"inline_code\">*/</span> so that the code segment works as intended?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR442172_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_code\">aw += weight;</span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_code\">aw += getWeight();</span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_code\">weight += aw;</span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_code\">return weight + aw;</span></p>"],"answer":2}]